136
00:13:29,522 --> 00:13:34,223
That's my concern, because I definitely like the idea of making sure that we notify more people.

137
00:13:34,303 --> 00:13:42,066
But I guess I'm worried about once you get into the neighborhoods, if you're doing something to increase the value of your property.

138
00:13:42,646 --> 00:13:44,086
